What is Power BI?

Power BI is a Business Intelligence (BI) tool developed by Microsoft that is used to analyze data and create interactive reports and dashboards.

Power BI converts raw data into meaningful information that helps businesses make better decisions.


ðŸ”¹ What is Business Intelligence (BI)?

Business Intelligence means:

Using data to understand business performance and support decision making.

Examples:

Which product sells the most?

Which month has highest sales?

Which region is performing best?

Why Power BI is Used?

To analyze large amounts of data

To create visual reports

To track business performance

To find trends and patterns

To save time and effort



